## Overview  

This project is a single-page application (SPA) with smooth scrolling and routing, designed to highlight my work as a Product Designer with a front-end background.  

Features:  
- Sticky glassmorphism navbar with reflective hover animation  
- Smooth scrolling navigation across sections (Home, About, Projects, Contact)  
- React Router integration (routes also map to sections for shareable URLs)  
- Custom About section showcasing my background and design approach  
- Project gallery with cards describing tools and outcomes  
- Contact form with styled input fields and focus states  
- Fully responsive (mobile to desktop)  

